      "type": "add",
      "item": {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "bc50ec52-4fc1-4948-a164-066de0ea7b75",
        "text": "The method arises out of the work of Ian Grigg completed in the mid-1990s in contributions to Ricardo, a system of assets transfers that was built in 1995-1996 by Systemics and included the pattern. The system and the design pattern was named after [[David Ricardo]] in honour of his seminal contribution to [[international trade theory]]."
      },
